node.text:
Watch to see how we capture Henry + Baloo’s special moments and learn some tips + tricks you can use to photograph your amazing pets! 

#ad Thanks to our friends @samsungmobile we filmed everything with our #GalaxyS21 Ultra for the new Master It creator classes, and wow ... it is incredible. Seriously can’t wait to share some more photos/videos with you and show you how to #MasterIt #withGalaxy

HAPPY 7th BIRTHDAY Henry!!!🎉

node.text:
Humans and furry friends you have to stream Turner & Hooch, an Original Series now streaming on @DisneyPlus! #ad This series is about Hooch, an amazing canine U.S. Marshall, who fights crime alongside his human BFF, Turner. They are besties that do everything together, even though their friendship was unlikely from the start.. just like us! 

Turner & Hooch chasing bad guys is as thrilling as seeing your friends at the dog park and Josh Peck, aka Turner, is so funny! Guaranteed to have a good belly laugh. If I weren’t climbing mountains and swimming in rivers, I’d want to be chasing bad guys just like Hooch. 5/5 Paws! -♥️ Henry 
#TurnerAndHoochSeries #DisneyPlus
